==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Denotative
<hw>De*not"a*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having power to
denote; designating or marking off.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Proper names are pre⟦eum⟧minently <qex>denotative</qex>; telling
us that such as object has such a term to denote it, but telling us
nothing as to any single attribute.</q> <rj><qau>Latham.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Denote</ent>⟦br⟧
